Text:
Tack för detta - har själv Lost masters-serien i original och tänkte lägga ut såväl dem som omslagen, men din torrent tog hand om det senare. Intressant att vissa användare kommenterar att du inte lagt ut själva musiken, när de själv inte har en enda torrent att dela. Keep up the good work!

Thanks! I've got the Lost Masters-serie on originalcd's and thought about putting them and the artwork out for dl, but your torrent took care of the artworkpart. Interesting that some users comment about you not putting out the music, when they themselves haven't got a single torrent to share. Keep up the good work!
the lost masters series was uploaded here on PB about a week before i put the artwork up, but disappeared for some reason. i haven't got the complete serie and not in lossless format.
